1 Spellcaster-Type Synchro Monster + 1 Spellcaster-Type monsterThis monster can only be Special Summoned by Fusion Summon (from the Extra Deck). When this card is Fusion Summoned, place 2 Spell Counters on it. This card gains 1000 ATK for each Spell Counter on it. Once per turn, you can remove 1 Spell Counter from your side of the field to activate one of the following effects: ● Select 1 card on the field, and destroy it. ● Draw 1 card.
